file_contents["CIS-C2-A1R_Prototype_Alpha1_Report.md"] = """# Prototype Alpha-1 Report\n\n**Document ID:** CIS-C2-A1R\n**CIS Layer:** PLLC\n**Centauri Phase:** Centauri-11\n**TRL Target:** 3–4\n**Grid Slot:** M-021\n**PRECISELIENS Node:** Mirror-6\n\n---\n\n## 1. Purpose\nDocument the Alpha-1 prototype, the first Phase I demonstration of functional capability under controlled but realistic conditions.\n\n## 2. Inputs\n- Alpha-0 Report\n- Phase I Workplan\n- Updated architectural assumptions\n- RFMA\n\n## 3. Outputs\n- Alpha-1 design description\n- Test results\n- Performance deltas vs. Alpha-0\n- Updated limitations list\n\n## 4. Method\n1. Implement Phase I feature set\n2. Conduct functional and environmental tests\n3. Compare results to Alpha-0 baseline\n4. Document anomalies and insights\n\n## 5. Mission Integration\n- Identifies which mission functions Alpha-1 can now support\n- Establishes early interface behavior\n- Provides data for Phase II justification\n\n## 6. TRL & SBIR Mapping\n- TRL: 3–4\n- SBIR: Phase I mid-stage\n\n## 7. Risks & Mitigations\n- **Risk:** Prototype instability\n  **Mitigation:** Add fallback logic in Mirror layer\n- **Risk:** Environmental mismatch\n  **Mitigation:** Increase fidelity of test conditions\n\n## 8. Change Log\n- 2026-05-17 — Alpha-1 baseline documented\n"""
